commit 6d830e4f6078510e4b5cbed55179d3c795813009
Author: Stephen Sherratt <stephen@sherra.tt>
Date:   Fri Oct 13 17:02:58 2023 +1100

    (pkg) refactor solver fields in workspace config
    
    Removes the `solver_env` section of the workspace config and replaces it
    with the individual fields of `solver_env` that can be set from there.
    Also the "repositories" field of `Solver_env.t` is removed so that that
    type just contains the variable environment used by the solver.
    
    Signed-off-by: Stephen Sherratt <stephen@sherra.tt>

